dct_title_s: City of Camden, New Jersey Plan showing Proposed Development of Spruce Street Property
dct_description_sm: Map shows Delaware River to Front Street and Spruce to Walnut in Camden City. Shows the proposed development of Spruce Street Property, pierhead and bulkhead lines, reinforced bulkheads, and property lines.
